1.5.0.name: drupal/d2c_analytics

security-coverage.message: Covered by Drupal's security advisory policy

1.5.0.description: Populates the database with statistics about your visitors and the QR Codes usage they made. This information will later be processed by consumer modules to produce graphs of your interest.
